Add the following to the /etc/ensuite/yencap/modules.xml file:
<modules xmlns:mon=urn:company:yencap:module:vermont:1.0>
<!-- other modules -->
	<module>
		<name>VERMONT</name>
		<xpath>/ycp:netconf/ycp:monitoring/mon:MonitorConfig</xpath>
		<namespace>urn:company:yencap:module:vermont:1.0</namespace>
		<cache-lifetime>10000</cache-lifetime>
	</module>
</modules>

Also update /etc/ensuite/yencap/rbac.xml file according to your security policy.